      <title>耶伦为拜登辩护，称其在会议中“极其高效”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/yellen-defends-biden-as-extremely-effective-in-meetings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在众议院听证会上，当被问及总统的精神敏锐度时，财政部长珍妮特·耶伦表示，她的老板乔·拜登在他们都参加的长时间会议中表现得“极其高效”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/yellen-defends-biden-as-extremely-effective-in-meetings</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 16:11:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大民意调查显示保守党领袖在经济问题上与特鲁多差距扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/conservative-leader-poilivere-widens-lead-over-trudeau-on-economy-nanos-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在谁将成为最佳经济管理者的问题上，加拿大保守党领袖在选民中领先优势扩大，凸显了总理贾斯汀·特鲁多面临的政治挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/conservative-leader-poilivere-widens-lead-over-trudeau-on-economy-nanos-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:50:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>林德纳的欧洲央行危机工具引发政策制定者担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/lindner-s-ecb-crisis-tool-doubts-stoke-dismay-among-policymakers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳 (Christian Lindner) 公开表达了对欧洲央行向法国提供危机援助的合法性的怀疑，这让欧洲决策圈感到不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/lindner-s-ecb-crisis-tool-doubts-stoke-dismay-among-policymakers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:02:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>知情人士称 Siddiq 将出任英国城市事务大臣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/tulip-siddiq-to-be-uk-s-city-minister-person-familiar-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 将任命图利普·西迪克 (Tulip Siddiq) 为英国金融城大臣，该职位属于财政部，将让她成为监管和倡导关键金融服务行业的核心人物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/tulip-siddiq-to-be-uk-s-city-minister-person-familiar-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:01:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国下一届政府将继承强劲增长势头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-s-next-government-is-set-to-inherit-resilient-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国经济今年预计将保持稳定增长，这将缓解下届政府面临的预算挑战。此前，法国提前大选导致出现悬浮议会，未来财政政策面临巨大不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-s-next-government-is-set-to-inherit-resilient-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:01:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登减缓民主党人叛逃速度，但选举忧虑依然存在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/biden-slows-democratic-defections-while-election-worries-persist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管在辩论表现糟糕之后，民主党内部对于拜登是否应继续担任白宫候选人仍存在严重分歧，但总统乔·拜登已经暂时减缓了众议院民主党人的公开叛逃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/biden-slows-democratic-defections-while-election-worries-persist</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 14:56:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特警告 G-7 禁止俄罗斯扣押其资产，并威胁出售其债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/saudi-arabia-veiled-threat-to-g7-over-russia-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，沙特阿拉伯今年早些时候曾私下暗示，如果七国集团决定扣押俄罗斯近 3000 亿美元的冻结资产，沙特阿拉伯可能会出售部分欧洲债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/saudi-arabia-veiled-threat-to-g7-over-russia-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 13:28:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>到 2030 年，英国可能需要额外 570 亿英镑绿色资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/uk-likely-needs-another-57-billion-for-green-investment-by-2030</link>
      <description><![CDATA[到 2030 年，英国可能需要高达 570 亿英镑（730 亿美元）的额外投资来发展关键产业，新一届工党政府认为这将有助于该国支持绿色就业增长并减少对碳的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/uk-likely-needs-another-57-billion-for-green-investment-by-2030</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 12:28:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国左翼呼吁马克龙盟友参与联合执政</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-s-left-appeals-to-macron-allies-to-gain-edge-in-coalition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[混乱的投票导致议会分裂，政治角逐愈演愈烈，法国社会党向埃马纽埃尔·马克龙领导的运动的部分议员伸出了橄榄枝。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-s-left-appeals-to-macron-allies-to-gain-edge-in-coalition</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 11:21:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约支持在发生海底袭击时通过重新路由到太空来拯救互联网的努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/nato-backs-effort-to-reroute-internet-to-space-in-event-of-subsea-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约正在帮助资助一个项目，该项目旨在寻找在欧洲海域传输民用和军事通信的海底电缆受到攻击时维持互联网运行的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/nato-backs-effort-to-reroute-internet-to-space-in-event-of-subsea-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 16:38:21 GMT</pubDate>
